      <span>2</span>
    <p style="margin-bottom: 0px; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 12px; line-height: normal; font-family: Helvetica;">To use as an overnight moisturizing mask: Apply a thin, even layer onto cleansed, damp skin. Leave on overnight then wipe off. Applying too much causes this mask to pill.</p> 
