</div><div class="stamped-reviews"><div class="stamped-review" id="stamped-review-42879669" data-product-id="5742111686811" data-rating="5" data-verified="">
    <div class="stamped-review-header">
        <div class="stamped-review-avatar" style="padding:0;" data-avatar="false">
            
            <div class="stamped-review-avatar-content">
                K
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="created">02/28/2021</div>
        <strong class="author">Kyra</strong> 
        <div class="review-location"><span class="stamped-location-flag"><img class="stamped-lazyload" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202im_/https://cdn.stamped.io/cdn/images/pixel.png" data-src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://cdn.stamped.io/cdn/flags/us.svg" width="15" height="13" alt="United States" onerror="this.style.display=&quot;none&quot;;"/></span> <span data-location="United States">United States</span></div>
        <div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stamped-review-content">
        <div class="stamped-review-recommend" data-is-recommend=""></div>
        <div class="stamped-review-body">

            <span class="stamped-starratings stamped-review-header-starratings" data-rating="5"> <i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i> </span>
            <div class="stamped-review-header-title">Super soft</div>
            <p class="stamped-review-content-body">I’ve been using this for about 2 months and I love it! I like to use it as a moisturizer and I layer it on top of my everyday moisturizer. I agree that it pills but that only happens if you use more product than advised. Also if you’re layering it like I do, go easy on your regular moisturizer before applying this bc it will pill! Other than that, this makes my face super soft and hasn’t made me break out. Also, 2 months in with this and the tube still has a lot of product so that’s a plus :)</p>

        <div class="stamped-review-options"></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-image">
                
            </div>
            <div class="stamped-review-product" style="display:none;"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://stamped.io/go/d3xXaWRnZXRNYWlufDE2MjgxMXxyfDQyODc5NjY50" rel="nofollow" target="_top">LIKE BUTTER</a></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-variant" style="display:none;"></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-footer">
                <div class="stamped-review-share"><div class="stamped-share-wrapper"><span class="stamped-share-icon" aria-label="Share" role="button" tabindex="0" rel="nofollow noopener"><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-share-alt"></i> Share</span><span class="stamped-share-links" style=""> &nbsp; | &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://www.facebook.com/dialog/share?app_id=222664514734026&amp;display=popup&amp;href=https%3a%2f%2fmy-topicals.myshopify.com%2fa%2freview%2ffacebookpost%3freviewId%3d42879669&amp;redirect_uri=https://stamped.io/shares?review_id=42879669" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Facebook</a> &nbsp;•&nbsp; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20using%20this%20for%20about%202%20months%20and%20I%20love%20it!%20I%20like%20to%20use%20it%20as%20a%20moisturizer%20and%20I%20layer%20it%20on%20top%20of%20my%20everyday%20moisturizer.%20I&amp;url=https%3a%2f%2fmy-topicals.myshopify.com%2fa%2freview%2ftwittercard%3freviewId%3d42879669" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Twitter</a></span></div></div>
