</div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</div><div class="stamped-review" id="stamped-review-42461881" data-product-id="5742111686811" data-rating="3" data-verified="">
    <div class="stamped-review-header">
        <div class="stamped-review-avatar" style="padding:0;" data-avatar="false">
            
            <div class="stamped-review-avatar-content">
                B
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="created">02/17/2021</div>
        <strong class="author">Ben</strong> 
        <div class="review-location"><span class="stamped-location-flag"><img class="stamped-lazyload" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202im_/https://cdn.stamped.io/cdn/images/pixel.png" data-src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://cdn.stamped.io/cdn/flags/us.svg" width="15" height="13" alt="United States" onerror="this.style.display=&quot;none&quot;;"/></span> <span data-location="United States">United States</span></div>
        <div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stamped-review-content">
        <div class="stamped-review-recommend" data-is-recommend=""></div>
        <div class="stamped-review-body">

            <span class="stamped-starratings stamped-review-header-starratings" data-rating="3"> <i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star-o "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star-o "></i> </span>
            <div class="stamped-review-header-title">Good but hard to use </div>
            <p class="stamped-review-content-body">I want to start by saying I love the philosophy of the brand, their ingredients, and their transparency. The moisteruizer was great when only applied to damp skin (water damp). But if I tried to lay it over ANY serums, it pilled. BADLY. and I also couldn’t layer a face oil over it, or it would pull. I love the consistency of it and it calmed down inflamed skin if used correctly, but it’s so hard to use that I won’t repurchase. For $32, I would like my moisteruizer to be easier to use.
</p>

        <div class="stamped-review-options"></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-image">
                
            </div>
            <div class="stamped-review-product" style="display:none;"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://stamped.io/go/d3xXaWRnZXRNYWlufDE2MjgxMXxyfDQyNDYxODgx0" rel="nofollow" target="_top">LIKE BUTTER</a></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-variant" style="display:none;"></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-footer">
                <div class="stamped-review-share"><div class="stamped-share-wrapper"><span class="stamped-share-icon" aria-label="Share" role="button" tabindex="0" rel="nofollow noopener"><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-share-alt"></i> Share</span><span class="stamped-share-links" style=""> &nbsp; | &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://www.facebook.com/dialog/share?app_id=222664514734026&amp;display=popup&amp;href=https%3a%2f%2fmy-topicals.myshopify.com%2fa%2freview%2ffacebookpost%3freviewId%3d42461881&amp;redirect_uri=https://stamped.io/shares?review_id=42461881" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Facebook</a> &nbsp;•&nbsp; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=I%20want%20to%20start%20by%20saying%20I%20love%20the%20philosophy%20of%20the%20brand%2C%20their%20ingredients%2C%20and%20their%20transparency.%20The%20moisteruizer%20was%20great%20when%20onl&amp;url=https%3a%2f%2fmy-topicals.myshopify.com%2fa%2freview%2ftwittercard%3freviewId%3d42461881" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Twitter</a></span></div></div>
