    </div>
</div><div class="stamped-review" id="stamped-review-42299259" data-product-id="5742111686811" data-rating="5" data-verified="">
    <div class="stamped-review-header">
        <div class="stamped-review-avatar" style="padding:0;" data-avatar="false">
            
            <div class="stamped-review-avatar-content">
                L
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="created">02/14/2021</div>
        <strong class="author">LA</strong> 
        <div class="review-location"><span class="stamped-location-flag"><img class="stamped-lazyload" src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202im_/https://cdn.stamped.io/cdn/images/pixel.png" data-src="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://cdn.stamped.io/cdn/flags/us.svg" width="15" height="13" alt="United States" onerror="this.style.display=&quot;none&quot;;"/></span> <span data-location="United States">United States</span></div>
        <div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stamped-review-content">
        <div class="stamped-review-recommend" data-is-recommend=""></div>
        <div class="stamped-review-body">

            <span class="stamped-starratings stamped-review-header-starratings" data-rating="5"> <i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-star "></i> </span>
            <div class="stamped-review-header-title">So Helpful!</div>
            <p class="stamped-review-content-body">I have terrible seasonal allergies that sometimes manifest in an uncomfortable red rash around my mouth. The cortisone cream that relieves this allergic reaction also dries out my skin so badly that it is nearly as uncomfortable as the rash itself. I bought Like Butter to use after the cortisone to help sooth my dried out, irritated skin and its so incredibly helpful! I love that its unscented so I can put it around my mouth and more sensitive areas on my face. Thank you so much for making this product. I know its made for eczema, but it has really saved my skin during my Cedar Fever freakouts.</p>

        <div class="stamped-review-options"></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-image">
                
            </div>
            <div class="stamped-review-product" style="display:none;"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://stamped.io/go/d3xXaWRnZXRNYWlufDE2MjgxMXxyfDQyMjk5MjU50" rel="nofollow" target="_top">LIKE BUTTER</a></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-variant" style="display:none;"></div>
            <div class="stamped-review-footer">
                <div class="stamped-review-share"><div class="stamped-share-wrapper"><span class="stamped-share-icon" aria-label="Share" role="button" tabindex="0" rel="nofollow noopener"><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-share-alt"></i> Share</span><span class="stamped-share-links" style=""> &nbsp; | &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://www.facebook.com/dialog/share?app_id=222664514734026&amp;display=popup&amp;href=https%3a%2f%2fmy-topicals.myshopify.com%2fa%2freview%2ffacebookpost%3freviewId%3d42299259&amp;redirect_uri=https://stamped.io/shares?review_id=42299259" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Facebook</a> &nbsp;•&nbsp; <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210303090202/https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=I%20have%20terrible%20seasonal%20allergies%20that%20sometimes%20manifest%20in%20an%20uncomfortable%20red%20rash%20around%20my%20mouth.%20The%20cortisone%20cream%20that%20relieves%20t&amp;url=https%3a%2f%2fmy-topicals.myshopify.com%2fa%2freview%2ftwittercard%3freviewId%3d42299259" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">Twitter</a></span></div></div>
                <div class="stamped-review-vote"><div class="stamped-rating-holder">Was this helpful? <a class="stamped-thumbs-up" data-rating="1" data-review-id="42299259" tabindex="0" aria-label="Rate review as helpful" role="button" data-votes="1"><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-thumbs-up">&nbsp;1</i></a><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><a class="stamped-thumbs-down" data-rating="-1" data-review-id="42299259" tabindex="0" aria-label="Rate review as not helpful" role="button" data-votes="0"><i class="stamped-fa stamped-fa-thumbs-down">&nbsp;0</i></a></div>
</div>
